videos.headline: Gaskin breaks out 64 yard run
videos.description: Myles Gaskin rushes 64 yards for a Washington first down.

videos.headline: Ahmed runs option for Washington TD
videos.description: Salvon Ahmed receives the pitch and runs it in for a Washington touchdown to push its lead over Oregon State to 14-3.

videos.headline: Browning lofts pass to Fuller for TD
videos.description: Jake Browning drops a pass right into Aaron Fuller's arms for the 17-yard Washington touchdown.

videos.headline: Browning finds wide-open Otton for TD
videos.description: Jake Browning connects with a wide-open Cade Otton in the end zone for a 21-yard Washington touchdown.

videos.headline: Luton connects with Hodgins for TD
videos.description: Jake Luton links up with Isaiah Hodgins, who barely makes it over the goal line for an Oregon State touchdown.

videos.headline: Choukair banks in 35-yd FG for Beavers
videos.description: Oregon State's Jordan Choukair banks in the 35-yard field goal kick off the upright post.

videos.headline: Gaskin stretches for Washington TD
videos.description: Washington runs play action and Jake Browning finds Myles Gaskin, who takes it in for the 10-yard touchdown.
